  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read the canonical wrapper produced by Wave 1 task 022: `src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/components/EmailComposer/wrappers/SendEmailDialog.tsx`. Confirm its prop signature matches FR-03 spec.</step>
    <step order="2">Read the current `src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/components/SendEmailDialog/SendEmailDialog.tsx`. Determine if Wave 1 task 022 already rewrote it inline OR if it still holds the legacy implementation.</step>
    <step order="3">Decide the integration path: (A) `SendEmailDialog/SendEmailDialog.tsx` is REWRITTEN inline to mount `<EmailComposer mount='dialog' />`, OR (B) `SendEmailDialog/SendEmailDialog.tsx` becomes a one-line re-export of `EmailComposer/wrappers/SendEmailDialog.tsx`. Prefer (B) for collapse to a single source of truth; record the choice in task notes.</step>
    <step order="4">Apply the chosen integration. If (B): replace `SendEmailDialog.tsx` body with `export { SendEmailDialog, type ISendEmailDialogProps } from '../EmailComposer/wrappers/SendEmailDialog';` and confirm `SendEmailDialog/index.ts` re-exports.</step>
    <step order="5">Confirm `src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/index.ts` top-level barrel exports `SendEmailDialog` and `ISendEmailDialogProps` from this path (do not introduce a second export source).</step>
